### Naming Conventions
- Views: `{Feature}View.swift` (e.g., `ProductDetailView.swift`)
- ViewModels: `{Feature}ViewModel.swift`
- Sections within views: `var {name}Section: some View`
- Subcomponents: `{Parent}.{Child}` (e.g., `HomeView.CategoryCard`)

