## ‚ö†Ô∏è ANTI-PATTERNS TO AVOID

1. **Don't use pure white (#FFFFFF)** - Always use off-white (#FAFAFA)
2. **Don't use bold on Georgia** - Stick to regular or medium
3. **Don't use large corner radius** - Max 12pt, prefer 0-4pt
4. **Don't use colored backgrounds on cards** - Keep neutral
5. **Don't use emoji or playful icons** - Keep it sophisticated
6. **Don't overuse gold accent** - It's for highlights only
7. **Don't use system blue** - Stay within the palette
8. **Don't use heavy shadows** - Prefer subtle borders or elevation
9. **Don't use Inter, Roboto, or SF Pro Display explicitly** - Use Georgia for display, system for body
10. **Don't animate everything** - Be selective and subtle

